  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-CON-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This package is an adversarial sample targeting W-CON-01: the decision record records outcome Accepted, yet two credibility factors (Model form and Model inputs) carry no requiredLevel or achievedLevel, leaving the acceptance decision without grounding in structured factor evidence.",
