      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software quality assurance practices must meet Gradation 4 for MRL 5 Class III device applications, including version control, test coverage, and audit trails.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver has documented version control and unit testing but lacks full audit trail and independent code review required at Gradation 4. Achieved level is 3."
