      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions must match COU operating envelope within defined tolerances for flow rate, rotational speed, and fluid properties.",
      "rationale": "Experimental data sourced from FDA benchmark dataset. Flow rates match COU envelope; however, fluid temperature during experiments differed by up to 2°C from nominal VAD operating temperature. Achieved level is 3."
