      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative comparison metrics (e.g., E%, NRMSE) must be computed between predicted and experimental hemolysis index values across all COU operating points.",
      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed at 5 operating points. Mean normalized error is 18%, exceeding the 10% threshold for Gradation 4. Achieved level is 3."
